OL,3,CTwo men sentenced after arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to prime minister
OL,6,FTwo men have been sentenced after
OL,7,Fbeing found guilty of three separate
OL,8,Farson attacks on properties and a car
OL,9,Flinked to the prime minister, Sir Keir
OL,10,FStarmer.
OL,12,FUkrainian Roman Lavrynovych, 22, has
OL,13,Fbeen sentenced to seven years in
OL,14,Fprison, while Romanian Stanislav
OL,15,FCarpiuc, 27, has been imprisoned for
OL,16,Ftwo years.
OL,18,FThe arson attacks took place in a
OL,19,Fresidential area of north London over
OL,20,Fthree nights in May 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
