OL,3,CTwo men sentenced after arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to prime minister
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn court, the lawyer representing
OL,12,FLavrynovych, James Scobie KC, stressed
OL,13,Fthe "shame" he had brought on his
OL,14,Ffamily in Ukraine.
OL,16,FMr Scobie said: "He gained absolutely
OL,17,Fnothing from this. He was used on any
OL,18,Fview ` utterly naive, utterly
OL,19,Fgullible, unthinking and a complete
OL,20,Fand utter foot soldier.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@KO]xD@QOU
