OL,3,CTwo men sentenced after arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to prime minister
OL,6,F"How worrying that is for us all that
OL,7,Fthere are individuals like this who
OL,8,Fare fodder for this type of
OL,9,Finfiltration who has not got a clue
OL,10,Fwho the 'big man' was ` turns who to
OL,11,Fbe the Prime Minister."
OL,13,FMeanwhile Carpiuc's lawyer, defence
OL,14,Fbarrister Shahid Rashid said his
OL,15,Fclient was "always the money man".
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@LOUwD@aO]
