OL,3,CTwo men sentenced after arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to prime minister
OL,6,FHe told the court: "His function was
OL,7,Fto realise the cryptocurrency. It is
OL,8,Falso important he was not going to get
OL,9,Fanything out of it. His motivation was
OL,10,Fhelping a friend out who needed money
OL,11,Fdesperately for his father's medical
OL,12,Ftreatment."
